OL,3,CConditions that led to disorder 'still
OL,4,Cthere and could escalate again'
OL,6,FLast year disorder spread in some
OL,7,Fparts of the UK in the wake of the
OL,8,FSouthport murders on July 29, after
OL,9,Ffalse rumours were spread online that
OL,10,Fthe suspect was an asylum seeker who
OL,11,Fhad arrived in the UK by boat.
OL,13,FMosques, community centres and
OL,14,Flibraries were attacked, while hotels
OL,15,Fhousing asylum seekers were also
OL,16,Ftargeted.
