OL,3,CConditions that led to disorder 'still
OL,4,Cthere and could escalate again'
OL,6,FDr Mulhall told the PA news agency: "I
OL,7,Fthink it's without question the most
OL,8,Fwidespread period of far-right
OL,9,Fviolence, certainly the post-war
OL,10,Fperiod and possibly beyond.
OL,12,F"What makes it more shocking, the
OL,13,Fspeed with which it's kind of stopped
OL,14,Fgetting talked about or it got written
OL,15,Foff as legitimate anger.
OL,17,F"This is a really seismic historical
OL,18,Fmoment in history, post-war Britain,
OL,19,Fand very, very quickly it fell off the
OL,20,Fradar."
