OL,6,FHe said the decentralised concept of
OL,7,Ffar-right activism makes it more
OL,8,Fcomplex "but I don't think it makes it
OL,9,Fany less far-right".
OL,11,FAt the height of the disorder, a fire
OL,12,Fwas fuelled outside a hotel housing
OL,13,Fasylum seekers in Manvers, near
OL,14,FRotherham, South Yorkshire, on August
OL,15,F4.
OL,17,FTwo men were handed nine-year prison
OL,18,Fsentences in connection with the fire,
OL,19,Fthe longest jail time of the hundreds
OL,20,Fof people convicted in relation to the
OL,21,Fcountrywide disorder.
