OL,6,FDr Mulhall said that during the period
OL,7,F"no-one was sleeping" as Hope Not Hate
OL,8,Fwere speaking to their sources in the
OL,9,Ffar-right and monitoring dozens of
OL,10,Fevents in real time.
OL,12,FThe team would then pass the
OL,13,Finformation to their policy
OL,14,Fcolleagues, who would contact
OL,15,Faccommodation or mosques they felt
OL,16,Fcould be attacked, or refugee
OL,17,Fcharities, to say they were worried
OL,18,Fabout forthcoming action.
