OL,6,F"In one sense, (it) was empowering. I
OL,7,Fthink by the end, lots of people
OL,8,Fobviously found it quite traumatic,
OL,9,Fsitting there for 11 days watching
OL,10,Freally traumatic stuff, people being
OL,11,Fbeaten, people being dragged out their
OL,12,Fcars."
OL,14,FDr Mulhall said the "quick crackdown"
OL,15,Fand quick arrests and sentencing of
OL,16,Frioters had a "damping effect" on the
OL,17,Ffar-right for the months that
OL,18,Ffollowed, and the organisation then
OL,19,Fhad a quiet period.
