OL,6,F"I think sometimes you can think of
OL,7,Fthe far-right like a volcano, you
OL,8,Fknow, once it explodes, sometimes it
OL,9,Ftakes some time for the magma chamber
OL,10,Fto rebuild up and the pressure to
OL,11,Fbuild before it pops again.
OL,13,F"That magma chamber I talk about,
OL,14,Funder-society of anger, prejudice,
OL,15,Fmisinformation, all those things, is
OL,16,Fstill there, which means it's a very,
OL,17,Fvery febrile time."
