OL,6,FHe added: "People are still furious.
OL,7,FIn some cases, they're more angry,
OL,8,Fwe're further into Labour government,
OL,9,Fthe economic conditions haven't got
OL,10,Fbetter.
OL,12,F"Which means that when you have a
OL,13,Ftrigger event, like an alleged
OL,14,Fhorrifying event in Epping, all of
OL,15,Fthose conditions are still there. That
OL,16,Fmeans that very, very quickly they can
OL,17,Fescalate.
