OL,7,F"escalation of violence" during
OL,8,Fprotests at the same site on July 13,
OL,9,F17, 20 and 24, involving hundreds of
OL,10,Fpeople.
OL,12,FMore than a dozen men have so far been
OL,13,Fcharged with offences ranging from
OL,14,Fviolent disorder to failing to remove
