OL,6,FWhile monitoring the events last week,
OL,7,FDr Mulhall said they picked up on 17
OL,8,Fprotests planned over the next 10
OL,9,Fdays, and were "slightly worried"
OL,10,Fabout planned protests for the weekend
OL,11,Fto come.
OL,13,FBut he added "this is not a mass
OL,14,Fuprising", with numbers across the
OL,15,Fcountry combined between 1,000 to
OL,16,F2,000 from activity seen so far.
