OL,6,FOn ways to curb the tensions, he said
OL,7,F"no-one" thinks that housing asylum
OL,8,Fseekers in hotels is a good idea, and
OL,9,Fhighlighted the role of technology and
OL,10,Fsocial media, when planning and
OL,11,Forganising of the far-right is
OL,12,Fhappening across online platforms.
OL,14,FIn the longer term he said the only
OL,15,Fthing that is going to work is a
OL,16,F"genuine social cohesion strategy".
OL,18,F"You're much less likely to believe
OL,19,Ffar-right misinformation about people
OL,20,Fthat live in your town if you know
OL,21,Fthem, if you've spent time with them."
